My Review of the book &ldquo;Make Your Point&rdquo;
Weak communication can cause you lose a HONDA CRV every week. Communication is crucial for success.
Take me for example. I have 10 meetings every day on average. Sometimes it is 14. Let’s make it a humble number. Take 5 meetings. Most of them have around 5 people on average and last for about an hour. Let’s take the 80$ per hour rate.
